reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing little stands!
reviews.reviewText: Was looking for bed side stands and went with these because they were cute and had the power strip in them. Super easy to put together! Took me about 25 minutes by myself to put them together. They are pretty sturdy and aesthetically pleasing. Will be ordering another set for my living room.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I have been searching for a nightstand for quite a while now and chose this one. I was initially worried it may be wobbly due to the legs but it actually came out quite sturdy. The legs are angled so that may be why they are not 100% sturdy enough for my liking. The plugs and charging base is what made me chose it since it's so convenient. Not a big fan of the cloth like drawers but it does the job. Not a bad nightstand for the price overall.

reviews.reviewText: My daughter absolutely loved her bedside table I got this because she had to fight to get her phone charger plugged in behind the headboard. The charger ports all worked great and I put it together by myself fairly easily. It’s very sturdy but yet light enough to move around!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful nightstand, easy to assemble!
reviews.reviewText: This nightstand is really cute. I’m in the process of re-organizing my master bedroom. I had a rolling cart for a nightstand, (new baby in the house), and it was convenient in the beginning. However, I have since had to add a few more things on top of my nightstand, such as a humidifier, and the rolling cart wasn’t cutting it anymore. This nightstand was very easy to put together. Took me about 30 minutes, maybe a little bit less. Having the plugs right underneath the drawer is so convenient. One of the plugs I use for my phone charger was a little bit too short from the wall outlet, but having it plugged in right under the nightstand makes it the perfect length. The finish is nice and looks beautiful in my bedroom!
